---
title: Japanese Sweet-Soy Tofu Curry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: You’ll be off to visit your happy place when you get a taste of this dish. Sweet with a touch of salt, that’s how we’re cooking up the tofu tonight. Add it to a katsu sauce curry with pan-fried veggies for crunch and colour. We wish you  safe travels to bliss.
